<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Server error - 500 error page">
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, follow">
    <title>500 - Server Error</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            color: #2d3748;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            border-radius: 1rem;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            max-width: 90%;
            width: 500px;
            animation: fadeIn 0.5s ease-out;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: #1a202c;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.125rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            color: #4a5568;
        }

        .loading-dots::after {
            content: '';
            animation: dots 1.5s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes dots {

            0%,
            20% {
                content: '';
            }

            40% {
                content: '.';
            }

            60% {
                content: '..';
            }

            80%,
            100% {
                content: '...';
            }
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(-20px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        a {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            background: #4299e1;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        a:hover {
            background: #3182ce;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(66, 153, 225, 0.3);
        }

        a:focus {
            outline: none;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(66, 153, 225, 0.5);
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }

            p {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }

            .container {
                padding: 1.5rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main class="container" role="main">
        <h1 aria-label="500 - Server Error">500 - Server Error</h1>
        <p>We're experiencing technical difficulties<span class="loading-dots"></span><br>
            Our team has been notified and is working on a fix.</p>
        <a href="/" role="button" aria-label="Return to homepage">Return to Homepage</a>
    </main>
</body>

</html>